*HEADING
 Single-element verification of umat_biofilm_visco.f (F=Fe*Fv*Fg)
 Growth (TEMP=alpha) against a clamped face, viscoelastic relaxation.
 Exercises Fg/Fv/Fe paths + the exact consistent tangent in a real
 Abaqus implicit increment loop.  UNSYMM=YES for the Jaumann tangent.
